---
source: tests/parser.rs
expression: "tree(\"row \\\\\\\\\\n[x] next\")"
---
ROOT@0..15
  PARAGRAPH@0..15
    WORD@0..3 "row"
    WHITESPACE@3..4 " "
    LINE_BREAK@4..6
      CONTROL_SYMBOL@4..6 "\\\\"
    NEWLINE@6..7 "\n"
    L_BRACKET@7..8 "["
    WORD@8..9 "x"
    R_BRACKET@9..10 "]"
    WHITESPACE@10..11 " "
    WORD@11..15 "next"
